---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="About MDRPedia ‚Äî The Impact Quotient"
    description="Cataloging humanity's greatest healers. The Forbes for Doctors, ranked by impact."
>
    <div class="about-container">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Quantifying the Unquantifiable</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">
                    For decades, society has obsessed over the Forbes Rich List.
                    We believe the true measure of a contribution isn't net
                    worth‚Äîit's <span class="highlight">Human Impact</span>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Manifesto Section -->
        <section class="mission">
            <div class="grid-2">
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>The Anti-Rich List</h2>
                    <p>
                        We are building the <strong>Forbes for Doctors</strong>,
                        but instead of dollars, we count lives saved, minds
                        taught, and breakthroughs made.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>MDRPedia</strong> is the world's first definitive
                        registry ranking medical professionals purely by their contribution
                        to humanity. From the surgeon who pioneered a life-saving
                        technique to the physician serving in a crisis zone, we honor
                        those who enrich the world, not just themselves.
                    </p>
                    <p class="branding-note">
                        *Sometimes referred to as <strong>MDpedia</strong> or <strong
                            >DrPedia</strong
                        > in medical journals and press.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <span class="number">950+</span>
                        <span class="label">Titans of Medicine</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <span class="number">100M+</span>
                        <span class="label">Lives Impacted</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- The Methodology -->
        <section class="methodology">
            <h2>The Impact Quotient (MDR Score)</h2>
            <p class="intro">
                How do you rank a doctor? We use a proprietary 4-Pillar System:
            </p>

            <div class="pillars">
                <div class="pillar">
                    <div class="icon">üî¨</div>
                    <h3>Intellectual Legacy</h3>
                    <p>
                        Research, citations, and inventions that changed medical
                        practice.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pillar">
                    <div class="icon">ü©∫</div>
                    <h3>Clinical Mastery</h3>
                    <p>
                        Verified surgeries, years of service, and patient
                        outcomes.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pillar">
                    <div class="icon">üåç</div>
                    <h3>Humanitarian Impact</h3>
                    <p>
                        Lives saved, crisis response, and service to the
                        underserved.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pillar">
                    <div class="icon">üéì</div>
                    <h3>Global Mentorship</h3>
                    <p>
                        The lineage of students trained and institutions built.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Rankings Explanation -->
        <section class="rankings-explainer">
            <div class="badge-preview">
                <div class="dummy-badge">
                    <span>#1</span> in Cardiology
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h2>Specialist Rankings</h2>
                <p>
                    Every doctor on MDRPedia is ranked within their specific
                    field. This ensures fair comparison‚Äîneurosurgeons are ranked
                    against neurosurgeons, oncologists against oncologists.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Achieving a <strong>Top 10</strong> rank in any specialty signifies
                    a level of excellence that defines a generation.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px 100px;
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
        padding: 100px 0;
        text-align: center;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle at center,
            rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #a5b4fc 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .highlight {
        color: var(--accent-purple);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }

    /* Grid Layouts */
    .grid-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 60px;
        align-items: center;
        margin: 80px 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .grid-2 {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
    }

    /* Sections */
    section {
        margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #fff;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Stat Box */
    .stat-box {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 40px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .stat .number {
        display: block;
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--accent-purple);
    }

    .stat .label {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* Pillars */
    .pillars {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 30px;
        margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .pillar {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .pillar:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    }

    .pillar .icon {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .pillar h3 {
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Ranking Explainer */
    .rankings-explainer {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 60px;
        background: linear-gradient(
            90deg,
            rgba(253, 185, 49, 0.05) 0%,
            transparent 100%
        );
        padding: 60px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        border-left: 4px solid #fdb931;
    }

    .dummy-badge {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700 0%, #fdb931 100%);
        color: #1a1a1a;
        padding: 20px 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(253, 185, 49, 0.2);
    }

    .dummy-badge span {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .branding-note {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-style: italic;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }
</style>
